	cont = 'xxx'

    html = etree.HTML(cont)

    # xpath匹配想要的内容
    element_ = html.xpath('//div[@class="paragraphs medium"]/p[1]')[0]      # 是个element对象

    # 最后如果不转码会是个 bytes 类型数据
    string = etree.tostring(element_, encoding='utf-8').decode('utf-8')     # 字符串类型
